	  THRESHOLD_CONVERT, as sensitivity is the reverse of threshold.
	  (read_preferences, prefs_widget_init): Change "threshold_entry" to
	  sensitivity_entry.
	  (prefs_widget_init): Call set_pixmap_file for the new pixmaps.
